The '''AKG C 518''' and '''M/C 518 ML''' is a miniature cardioid condenser clamp-on microphone.The '''C 518 M''' is for use with an external phantom power supply. The '''C 518 ML''' uses the B 29 L battery power supply, AKG WMS Series bodypack transmitters, or the MPA V L adapter for power.
